column1: This data is provided to meet the data availability requirements for a scientific publication. Data is derived from NIH's internal datasets and from Digital Science's Dimensions Platform. Data from Digital Science is based on metadata as of March 2024 from Digital Science's Dimensions platform, available at https://app.dimensions.ai/. Access was granted under license agreement with the National Cancer Institute. Researchers interested in exploring the data further should visit the Dimensions platform website.
